dish_name: just as they fry it "down on the farm" -donahoe's farm style chicken dinner- you begin with a pineapple sherbert fruit cup, then picture yourself a platter of piping hot fried  spring chicken (fried as they fry it "down on the farm") with that buttery, golden crispness- and along with the chicken comes a gravy boat of thick, rich chicken gravy, then a bowl of light fluffy mashed potatoes with the center hollowed out into a pool of melting butter.- of course, there's corn-on-the-cob, served with plenty of butter- a bowl of that tasty sour cream slaw(the farmer's favorite).- tasty dinner rolls, corn muffins, butter and old-fashioned apple butter in abundance.- then choose your favorite dessert from a large variety- and you may finish your dinner with donahoe's famous coffee with rich cream, tea (hot or cold), milk or buttermilk.- eat all you want- donahoe's wants you to feel that you've had a real feast.
